%203%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6595824fec62ab5daf80478e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20view%20of%20scene%20after%20explosions%20in%20Kerman%20City%2C%20Iran%20on%20Jan.%203%2C%202024.%3Cp%3EStringer%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20string%20of%20attacks%20by%20the%20ISIS%20affiliate%20that%20has%20been%20targeting%20Iran%20for%20five%20years.%20The%20first%20was%20a%20two-pronged%20operation%20against%20the%20Iranian%20parliament%20and%20Ayatollah%20Khomeini's%20mausoleum%20in%20the%20capital%2C%20Tehran%2C%20in%202017%2C%20that%20left%2016%20people%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIranian%20authorities%20say%20they%20have%20identified%20the%20alleged%20ringleader%20responsible%20for%20orchestrating%20the%20bombings.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Intelligence%20said%20that%20the%20main%20suspect%2C%20operating%20under%20the%20alias%20Abdollah%20Tajiki%2C%20is%20a%20Tajik%20national%20who%20illegally%20entered%20Iran%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThirty-five%20suspects%20across%20various%20provinces%20have%20also%20been%20apprehended%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20bombings%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Iranian%20intelligence%20ministry%20sought%20to%20blame%20its%20old%20enemy%20Israel%20for%20the%20atrocity%20and%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Firan-names-alleged-bombmaker-behind-isis-attack-says-1-of-2-bombers-is-tajik-israeli%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20the%20bombers%20had%20Israeli%20citizenship%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Times%20of%20Israel%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Slavin%20said%20the%20slaughter%20at%20Kerman%20did%20not%20bear%20the%20hallmarks%20of%20an%20Israeli%20covert%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsrael%20has%20done%20a%20lot%20against%20Iran%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Slavin.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20assassinated%20nuclear%20scientists%2C%20it's%20carried%20out%20cyber%20sabotage%20of%20nuclear%20facilities%2C%20it's%20stolen%20documents%20from%20Iran%2C%20highly%20sensitive%20nuclear%20archives%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20But%20it%20it%20has%20not%20at%20least%2C%20in%20my%20experience%2C%20taken%20part%20in%20these%20kinds%20of%20terrorist%20attacks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20intelligence%20corroborated%20ISIS'%20role.%20White%20House%20spokesman%20John%20Kirby%20said%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Firan-vows-revenge-after-biggest-attack-since-1979-revolution-2024-01-04%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20was%20in%20%26quot%3Bno%20position%20to%20doubt%20Islamic%20State's%20claim%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20that%20it%20was%20responsible%2C%20per%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EISIS%20plotted%20a%20revenge%20attack%20because%20they%20hated%20Iran's%20top%20commander%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224669%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Qassem%20Soleimani%20Iran%20Revolutionary%20Guard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5878fbedee14b61c008b817d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223113%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERevolutionary%20Guard%20Gen.%20Qassem%20Soleimani%2C%20center%2C%20attends%20a%20meeting%20with%20Supreme%20Leader%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%20and%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20commanders%20in%20Tehran%2C%20Iran%2C%20September%2018%2C%202016.%20As%20Saudi%20Arabia%20holds%20a%20naval%20drill%20in%20the%20strategic%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%20Soleimani%2C%20a%20powerful%20Iranian%20general%20was%20quoted%2C%20Wednesday%2C%20Oct.%205%2C%202016%2C%20by%20the%20semi-official%20Fars%20and%20Tasnim%20news%20agencies%20as%20suggesting%20the%20kingdom's%20deputy%20crown%20prince%20is%20so%20%26quot%3Bimpatient%26quot%3B%20he%20may%20kill%20his%20own%20father%20to%20take%20the%20throne.%20While%20harsh%20rhetoric%20has%20been%20common%20between%20the%20two%20rivals%20since%20January%2C%20the%