out.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeet-the-typical-hybrid-worker-income-profession-age-2023-10%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHybrid%2520workers%2520are%2520more%2520likely%2520to%2520be%2520millennial%2520men%26amp%3Btext%3Dis%2520millennial%2520men.-%2CData%2520from%2520the%2520WFH%2520Research%2520Project%2520and%2520the%2520Survey%2520of%2Cwith%252019.5%2525%2520of%2520surveyed%2520women.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EWorkers%20who%20go%20into%20the%20office%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20get%20face%20time%20with%20upper%20management%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20in-person%20meetings%20or%20casual%20office%20conversations%20%E2%80%94%20which%20can%20increase%20their%20odds%20of%20scoring%20a%20promotion.%20Only%2042%25%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-workers-less-likely-promotions-raises-happier-wfh-rto-survey-2023-12%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520survey%2520published%2520last%2520Tuesday%2Chybrid%2520workers%2520received%2520a%2520promotion%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efully%20remote%20workers%20received%20a%20promotion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023%2C%20compared%20to%2054%25%20of%20hybrid%20workers%20and%2055%25%20of%20full-time%20office%20workers%20in%20a%20survey%20of%201%2C190%20full-time%20employees%20from%20Resume%20Builder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExecutives%20seem%20to%20believe%20that%20simply%20showing%20up%20at%20the%20office%20demonstrates%20that%20a%20worker%20cares%20about%20their%20job.%20Around%2090%25%20of%20CEOs%20in%20the%20US%20said%20they%20would%20reward%20employees%20who%20try%20to%20come%20into%20the%20office%20with%20better%20assignments%2C%20raises%2C%20or%20promotions%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkpmg.com%2Fkpmg-us%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fkpmg%2Fpdf%2F2023%2F2023-CEO-Outlook-report-final.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esurvey%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20consulting%20firm%20KPMG%20of%201%2C325%20CEOs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20workers%20who%20go%20into%20the%20office%20are%20also%20more%20likely%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feffective-feedback-should-be-a-two-way-conversation-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereceive%20helpful%20feedback%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Economist%20Emma%20Harrington%20conducted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscholar.harvard.edu%2Ffiles%2Fpallais%2Ffiles%2Fpower_of_proximity.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estudy%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20software%20engineers%20at%20a%20Fortune%20500%20company%2C%20and%20found%20that%20remote%20workers%2C%20especially%20female%20workers%2C%20are%20less%20likely%20to%20receive%20feedback%20than%20those%20who%20were%20working%20near%20their%20teammates.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20junior%20women%20are%20working%20near%20their%20co-workers%2C%20they're%20also%20more%20likely%20to%20receive%20feedback%20from%20more%20people%2C%20Harrington%20explained%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hoover.org%2Fresearch%2Fpower-proximity-conversation-emma-harrington-remote-work%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epodcast%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Hoover%20Institute.%20%26quot%3BIt%20does%20seem%20consistent%20with%20a%20story%20that%20when%20you're%20remote%20and%20you're%20a%20woman%20you%20just%20don't%20feel%20that%20comfortable%20asking%20for%20this%20additional%20feedback%20and%20advice%2C%26quot%3B%20Harrington%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20or%20not%20this%20is%20a%20good%20thing%20is%20still%20to%20be%20decided%20though.%20Remote%20work%20has%20helped%20boost%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwomen-are-working-at-record-highs-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewomen%20in%20the%20workforce%20to%20record%20levels%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20the%20data%20is%20mixed%20on%20whether%20remote%20or%20hybrid%20workers%20are%20more%20productive.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20some%20proximity%20bias%20going%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20Bloom%20told%20The%20Journal.%20%26quot%3BI%20literally%20call%20it%20discrimination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstanford-economist-hybrid-office-workers-more-successful-promotions-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705236841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a30374dcdb354a985775de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstanford-economist-hybrid-office-workers-more-successful-promotions-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Stanford%20economics%20professor%20said%20workers%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20get%20feedback%2C%20better%20assignments%2C%20and%20raises%20if%20they%20show%20up%20at%20the%20office.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lvaranasi%40insider.com%20(Lakshmi%20Varanasi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstanford-economist-hybrid-office-workers-more-successful-promotions-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Buffalo%20Bills%20QB%20Josh%20Allen%20makes%20and%20spends%20his%20millions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222349%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Josh%20Allen%20gets%20set%20to%20pass%20against%20the%20Jacksonville%20Jaguars.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a17d796979d7371822e9d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221761%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJosh%20Allen.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FPhelan%20M.%20Ebenhack%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJosh%20Allen%20is%20one%20of%20the%20top%20quarterbacks%20in%20the%20NFL%20and%20he's%20paid%20accordingly.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%206-foot-5%20superstar%20has%20already%20earned%20nine%20figures%20over%20six%20seasons%20with%20the%20Buffalo%20Bills.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C