E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAllen%20navigated%20an%20improbable%20route%20from%20his%20rural%20hometown%20in%20California%20to%20the%20pros.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222277%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Josh%20Allen%20throws%20a%20pass%20with%20the%20Wyoming%20Cowboys.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a1905bdcdb354a98573cfb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221708%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJosh%20Allen%20throws%20a%20pass%20with%20the%20Wyoming%20Cowboys.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FRyan%20Kang%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20many%20of%20the%20NFL's%20top%20stars%2C%20Allen%20graduated%20from%20high%20school%20without%20a%20single%20Division-I%20scholarship%20offer%20and%20opted%20to%20spend%20a%20year%20at%20a%20nearby%20junior%20college%20to%20garner%20interest%20from%20major%20football%20programs.%20Through%20just%2010%20games%20in%20his%20lone%20season%20at%20Reedley%20College%2C%20Allen%20threw%20for%202%2C055%20yards%20and%2026%20touchdowns%20with%20only%20five%20interceptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20only%20two%20Football%20Bowl%20Subdivision%20(FBS)%20schools%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0Eastern%20Michigan%20and%20Wyoming%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0offered%20him%20a%20scholarship%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Db6697a3903371bc7e01833042726454d190f4bc4721a8b43b5f62e802a845fd7%26postID%3D65a17d33d137673d8c9aced4%26postSlug%3Djosh-allen-net-worth-bills-quarterback-earns-millions%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.espn.com%252Fcollege-football%252Fstory%252F_%252Fid%252F20117075%252Fwyoming-cowboys-josh-allen-goes-unknown-no-1-pick-nfl-draft-buzz%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20ESPN%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20when%20Allen%20traveled%20to%20Laramie%20to%20visit%20the%20Cowboys'%20home%20turf%2C%20Eastern%20Michigan%20made%20the%20decision%20on%20Allen's%20behalf%20by%20pulling%20his%20offer%3B%20Wyoming%20it%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20him%20some%20time%20to%20find%20success%20with%20the%20Cowboys.%20Allen%20broke%20his%20collar%20bone%20just%20two%20games%20into%20his%20career%20at%20Wyoming%2C%20ending%20his%20first%20season%20just%20as%20it%20was%20beginning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20following%20year%2C%20Allen%20started%20the%20season%20as%20the%20Cowboys'%20starter%20under%20center%20and%20enjoyed%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20breakout%20college%20season.%20He%20threw%20for%203%2C203%20yards%20and%2028%20touchdowns%20with%2015%20interceptions%2C%20per%20ESPN.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAllen%20spent%20one%20more%20season%20at%20Wyoming%2C%20and%20while%20his%20output%20fell%2C%20his%20efficiency%20improved%20considerably.%20This%20shift%20offered%20the%20Buffalo%20Bills%20the%20assurance%20they%20needed%20to%20trade%20up%20in%20the%202018%20NFL%20Draft%20and%20nab%20Allen%3B%20they%20selected%20the%20budding%20star%20with%20the%20seventh%20overall%20pick%20of%20the%20draft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHe's%20since%20proven%20himself%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20top%20quarterbacks%20in%20the%20NFL.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Josh%20Allen%20scrambles%20against%20the%20New%20England%20Patriots.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a187256979d7371822f27c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJosh%20Allen.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FAdrian%20Kraus%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAllen%20started%20his%20NFL%20career%20as%20a%20backup%20in%20Buffalo.%20But%20after%20starting%20quarterback%20Nathan%20Peterman%20struggled%20early%20that%20season%2C%20Allen%20took%20over%20and%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0aside%20from%20injuries%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0never%20relinquished%20the%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20led%20the%20Bills%20to%20the%20playoffs%20in%202019%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0his%20first%20full%20season%20as%20a%20starter%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0with%203%2C000%2B%20passing%20yards%2C%2020%20passing%20touchdowns%2C%20and%20nin