0sequence%20here%2C'%20and%20we%20just%20had%20to%20build%20it%20out%20to%20make%20it%20unique%20for%20'Lift%2C'%26quot%3B%20Gray%20told%20Business%20Insider%20of%20the%20script%20in%20a%20recent%20interview.%20%26quot%3BIt%20definitely%20pisses%20me%20off%20when%20that%20happens.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20he%20had%20a%20great%20team%20around%20to%20help%20craft%20the%20two%20fight%20sequences.%20Gray%20explained%20to%20BI%20how%20he%20and%20his%20team%20pulled%20it%20all%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Airplane%20set%20in%20Lift%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a027badcdb354a9856c96c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221182%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20A380%20set%20for%20%26quot%3BLift.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20huge%20Airbus%20A380%20set%20was%20built%20to%20capture%20the%20first%20fight%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%26quot%3BLift%2C%26quot%3B%20Kevin%20Hart%20plays%20Cyrus%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20a%20group%20of%20thieves%20who%20attempt%20to%20steal%20%24500%20million%20in%20gold%20from%20a%20passenger%20plane%20mid-flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Cyrus%20and%20his%20team%20must%20also%20combat%20a%20team%20of%20terrorists%2C%20who%20are%20protecting%20the%20gold%20on%20the%20plane.%20Toward%20the%20end%20of%20the%20movie%2C%20Hart%20and%20his%20ex-girlfriend%20Abby%20(Gugu%20Mbatha-Raw)%20have%20to%20take%20on%20the%20bad%20guys%20on%20two%20separate%20occasions%20on%20two%20different%20planes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGray%20said%20he%20leaned%20heavily%20on%20his%20second-unit%20director%20and%20stunt%20coordinator%2C%20Steve%20Griffin%2C%20to%20help%20him%20develop%20the%20fight%20sequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20decided%20the%20first%20flight%20should%20be%20set%20in%20a%20large%20Airbus%20A380.%20A%20section%20of%20the%20aircraft%20was%20built%20on%20a%20sound%20stage%20and%20included%20an%20immaculate%20first-class%20section%20and%20a%20stairwell%20down%20to%20coach%20seating%20so%20that%20the%20action%20could%20flow%20through%20both%20areas%20of%20the%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20multiple%20fights%20are%20going%20on%20simultaneously%2C%20Gray%20said%20the%20only%20way%20for%20it%20to%20work%20was%20to%20have%20the%20setting%20be%20a%20huge%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20trying%20to%20get%20a%20cast%20and%20a%20crew%20and%20multiple%20cameras%20in%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20couldn't%20do%20that%20in%20a%20regular-sized%20plane.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20on%20the%20roof%20of%20a%20plane%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a028d36979d737182284f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22958%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fight%20had%20to%20feel%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gray.%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EGray%20wanted%20a%20completely%20different%20feel%20for%20the%20other%20fight%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGray%20knew%20he%20needed%20a%20complete%20change%20of%20scenery%20and%20all-new%20choreography%20for%20the%20second%20action%20sequence%20because%2C%20as%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you've%20seen%20one%20punch%2C%20you've%20seen%20them%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20scene%2C%20Cyrus%20and%20Abby%20have%20been%20captured%20and%20the%20bad%20guys%20have%20taken%20over%20the%20private%20jet%20Cyrus'%20team%20was%20using.%20They%20put%20their%20captives%20into%20the%20jet%20and%20take%20off%20again.%20While%20in%20the%20sky%2C%20Cyrus%20and%20Abby%20duke%20it%20out%20with%20the%20terrorists%20again%2C%20but%20this%20time%2C%20the%20plane%20goes%20out%20of%20control%20and%20spirals%20360%20degrees%2C%20twisting%20and%20turning%20everyone%20in%20the%20cabin%20like%20laundry%20in%20a%20dryer.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20shoot%20the%20sequence%2C%20the%20A380%20plane%20had%20to%20be%20completely%20dismantled%20on%20the%20sound%20stage%2C%20with%20the%20private%20jet%20set%20being%20built%20in%20its%20place.%20While%20that%20happened%2C%20Gray%20and%20production%20designer%20Dominic%20Watkins%20came%20up%20with%20a%20different%20vibe%20for%20the%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20important%20to%20design%20the%20private%20jet%20in%20a%20way%20that%20it%20didn't%20feel%20like%20the%20A380%2C%20so%20everything%20down%20to%20the%20color%20palette%20had%20to%20feel%20different.%20The%20shooting%20coverage%20had%20to%20feel%20different.%20The%20fight%20had%20to%20feel%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20Gray%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20differentiate%20the%20two%20planes%20further%2C%20the%20jet%20has%20a%20stripper%20pole%20that%20comes%20out%20of%20the%20floor%2C%20which%20Cyrus%20and%20Abby%20swing%20from%20while%20fighting.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kevin%20Hart%20getting%20his%20face%20pushed%20against%20a%20wall%20of%20a%20plane%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a02959dcdb354a9856ca1b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22958%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E(L-R)%20Kevin%20Hart%20and%20Burn%20Gorman%20in%20%26quot%3BLift.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EKevin%20Hart%20and%20Gugu%20Mbatha-Raw%20did%20many%20of%20their%20own%20stunts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20coming%20up%20with%20the%20fight%20sequences%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20effort%2C%20Gray%20said%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20was%20keeping%20his%20actors%20safe%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20since%20Hart%20and%20Mbatha-Raw%20did%20many%20of%20their%20own%20stunts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20set%20is%20moving.%20It's%20doing%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20that%20you%20ordinarily%20wouldn't%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20if%20you're%20having%20a%20fight%20on%20the%20street%2C%26quot%3B%20Gray%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20trying%20to%20create%20an%20environment%20t