o%20now%20they're%20figuring%20out%3A%20Is%20the%20best%20defense%20a%20good%20offense%3F%20Meaning%2C%20is%20the%20best%20defense%20to%20now%20challenge%20the%20constitutional%20structure%20of%20the%20NLRB%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20request%20for%20a%20preliminary%20injunction%20filed%20against%20the%20NLRB%2C%20SpaceX%20argues%20that%20the%20judges%20overseeing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwrongful-termination-cases-employment-attorney-rejections-win-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrongful%20termination%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%20should%20not%20be%20able%20to%20determine%20whether%20SpaceX%20illegally%20fired%20its%20employees%20until%20the%20federal%20government%20rules%20on%20the%20company's%20constitutional%20questions%20surrounding%20the%20NLRB's%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpaceX%20has%20filed%20this%20action%20to%20avoid%20serious%20and%20irreparable%20injuries%20that%20it%20will%20otherwise%20suffer%20from%20being%20subjected%20to%20an%20unconstitutional%20administrative%20proceeding%2C%26quot%3B%20SpaceX's%20request%20reads.%20%26quot%3BDefendants%20are%20currently%20prosecuting%20and%20presiding%20over%20such%20a%20proceeding%20accusing%20SpaceX%20of%20violating%20federal%20law.%20Because%20the%20structure%20of%20that%20proceeding%20violates%20the%20United%20States%20Constitution%20under%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20Fifth%20Circuit%20precedent%2C%20SpaceX%20respectfully%20requests%20an%20order%20halting%20the%20NLRB%20proceedings%20unless%20and%20until%20the%20constitutional%20defects%20are%20remedied.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20lawyers%20go%20on%20to%20argue%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3ENLRB%20judges%20and%20board%20members%20are%20unconstitutionally%20protected%20from%20removal%20from%20office%20by%20the%20President%2C%20in%20violation%20of%20Article%20II%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3ENLRB%20proceedings%20violate%20SpaceX's%20right%20to%20a%20jury%20trial%20by%20ruling%20on%20private%20matters%20outside%20the%20court%20system%2C%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20Seventh%20Amendment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NLRB%20%26quot%3Btransgresses%20the%20separation%20of%20powers%20and%20violates%20SpaceX's%20due-process%20rights%26quot%3B%20by%20%26quot%3Bexercising%20prosecutorial%2C%20legislative%2C%20and%20adjudicatory%20authority%20within%20the%20same%20proceeding.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20novel%2C%20aggressive%20approach%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJerry%20Cutler%2C%20a%20labor%20and%20employment%20attorney%2C%20and%20lecturer%20at%20Columbia%20University%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20BI%20that%20the%20constitutionality%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnlrb-rules-that-employers-cant-stifle-speech-for-severance-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Labor%20Relations%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20established%20the%20foundation%20of%20its%20enforcement%20board%2C%20the%20NLRB%2C%20has%20been%20challenged%20a%20few%20times%20over%20the%20years%2C%20including%20shortly%20after%20it%20was%20enacted%20in%201935.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20never%20successfully%2C%20to%20my%20knowledge%2C%20or%20on%20the%20somewhat%20novel%20grounds%20SpaceX%20has%20asserted%20in%20its%20lawsuit%2C%26quot%3B%20Cutler's%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECutler%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20arguments%20made%20in%20SpaceX's%20suit%20against%20the%20NLRB%20closely%20resemble%20a%20recent%20argument%20against%20the%20board's%20authority%20published%20in%20November%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffedsoc.org%2Fcommentary%2Ffedsoc-blog%2Fis-the-nlrb-unconstitutional-the-courts-may-finally-decide%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFederalist%20Society%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20conservative%20legal%20group%20advocates%20for%20a%20textualist%20and%20originalist%20interpretation%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWimmer%20called%20SpaceX's%20approach%20an%20%26quot%3Baggressive%2C%20all-in%20legal%20challenge%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20raises%20unique%20constitutional%20questions%20regarding%20the%20authority%20of%20the%20NLRB%20to%20rule%20on%20issues%20relating%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-illegally-denied-benefits-unionized-workers-claims-nlrb-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanager-employee%20relations%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20existence%20of%20federal%20enforcement%20agencies%20in%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20filing%20the%20case%20in%20Texas%2C%20Wimmer%20added%2C%20it%20appears%20SpaceX%20is%20attempting%20to%20have%20its%20case%20heard%20in%20front%20of%20a%20more%20receptive%20audience%20compared%20to%20more%20worker-defensive%20courts%20in%20California%2C%20where%20the%20alleged%20wrongful%20firings%20took%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NLRB%2C%20in%20response%20to%20SpaceX's%20suit%2C%20has%20argued%20the%20case%20should%20be%20heard%20in%20California.%20If%20the%20NLRB%20is%20unsuccessful%20in%20getting%20the%20case%20moved%2C%20Wimmer%20said%2C%20he%20expects%20a%20relatively%20swift%20decision%20in%20favor%20of%20Musk%20that%20the%20NLRB%20would%20then%20need%20to%20appeal%20to%20overturn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPossible%20impacts%20of%20a%20SpaceX%20win%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESpaceX's%20legal%20challenge%20is%20not%20limited%20to%20this%20case%20alone%2C%20Wimmer%20told%20BI%2C%20but%20is%20rather%20an%20attack%20against%20the%20agency%20structure%20%26quot%3Bthat%20will%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20every%20case%20if%20they're%20successful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20SpaceX%20wins%20its%20suit%20against%20the%20NLRB%2C%20Wimmer%20said%20it%20would%20mean%20that%20Congress%20would%20have%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20reconstitute%20the%20labor%20relation%20board%2C%20as%20well%20as%20how%20other%20federal%20agencies%20are%20structured.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20future%20of%20federal%20enforcement%20agencies%20coming%20into%20question%20due%20to%20the%20potential%20success%20of%20SpaceX's%20suit%20against%20the%20NLRB%2C%20past%20decisions%20made%20by%20those%20agencies%20could%20also%20come%20under%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20National%20Labor%20Relations%20Board%20is%20the%20body%20that%20conducts%20the%20secret%20ballot%20elections%2C%20determines%20if%20they've%20been%20properly%20conducted%2C%20investigates%20complaints%20of%20unfair%20labor%20practices%2C%20prosecutes%20those%20complaints%2C%20and%20decides%20whether%20the%20prosecution%20is%20successful%20or%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Wimmer%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20at%20stake%20to%20this%20challenge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-spacex-national-labor-relations-board-lawsuit-nlrb-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705234801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a34ea4dcdb354a985776f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-spacex-national-labor-relations-board-lawsuit-nlrb-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22SpaceX%20filed%20suit%20against%20the%20NLRB%20alleging%20its%20proceedings%20are%20unconstitutional%20after%20the%20NLRB%20argued%20SpaceX%20violated%20federal%20labor%20laws.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-spacex-national-labor-relations-board-lawsuit-nlrb-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20business%20partner%20ended%20our%20relationship%20via%20email%20and%20outlined%20everything%20wrong%20with%20me.%20She%20still%20wanted%20to%20be%20friends.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224915%5C%22%20