money%20from%20their%20property%20would%20be%20nice%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20why%20they%20bought%20it%20or%20started%20Akiyamart.%20Their%20goal%20was%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20in%20Japan%20and%20show%20foreigners%20that%20homeownership%20can%20be%20achieved%20with%20a%20lower%20barrier%20of%20entry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20so%20many%20friends%20my%20age%20who%20are%20frustrated%20that%20they%20can't%20buy%20a%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20Kurosawa%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20kind%20of%20waving%20to%20my%20generation%20like%2C%20'Hey%2C%20there's%20another%20alternative.'%20It's%20not%20in%20America%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20really%20comfortable%20place%20that%20you%20could%20live%20and%20raise%20a%20family%20and%20live%20a%20very%20high%20quality%20of%20life%20without%20the%20financial%20stresses%20of%20living%20in%20the%20US.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20you%20bought%20a%20cheap%20home%20in%20Japan%E2%80%94%20or%20anywhere%20abroad%3F%20Business%20Insider%20wants%20to%20hear%20from%20you.%20Reach%20out%20to%20reporter%20Jordan%20Pandy%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajpandy%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ejpandy%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeople-moving-buying-abandoned-homes-japan-let-foreigners-own-home-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705233181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a04ed2dcdb354a9856e494%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeople-moving-buying-abandoned-homes-japan-let-foreigners-own-home-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Foreigners%20see%20Japan's%20empty%20houses%20as%20a%20way%20to%20be%20homeowners%20for%20as%20little%20as%20%2423%2C000.%20Moving%20there%20allows%20them%20a%20more%20adventurous%20and%20affordable%20life.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpandy%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Pandy)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeople-moving-buying-abandoned-homes-japan-let-foreigners-own-home-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maldives%20Asks%20India%20To%20Withdraw%20Military%20Personnel%20By%20March%2015%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaldives%20President%C2%A0Mohamed%20Muizzu%20has%20given%20a%20deadline%20to%20India%20to%20withdraw%20its%20troops%20from%20the%20island%20nation.%20The%20Maldivian%20President%20said%20the%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20should%20leave%20the%20nation%20by%20March%2015.%20The%20development%20comes%20a%20few%20days%20after%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20met%20Xi%20Jinping%20on%20his%20first%20state%20visit%20to%20China%20after%20being%20elected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbdulla%20Nazim%20Ibrahim%2C%20the%20public%20policy%20secretary%20at%20the%20President's%20Office%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIndian%20military%20personnel%20cannot%20stay%20in%20the%20Maldives.%20This%20is%20the%20policy%20of%20President%20Dr%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20and%20that%20of%20this%20administration.%26quot%3B%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20around%2088%20Indian%20troops%20are%20present%20in%20Maldives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maldives%20President's%20deadline%20comes%20almost%20two%20months%20after%20he%20called%20for%20a%20withdrawal%20of%20Indian%20troops%20and%20said%20the%20nation%20%26quot%3Bhas%20to%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20no%20presence%20of%20a%20foreign%20military%20on%20their%20soil%26quot%3B.%20The%20current%20Maldivian%20President%20came%20to%20power%20with%20his%20%26quot%3BIndia%20Out%26quot%3B%20campaign%20and%20is%20considered%20close%20to%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia-Maldives%20Diplomatic%20Row%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaldives%20and%20India%20have%20set%20up%20a%20high-level%20core%20group%20to%20negotiate%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20troops.%20The%20group%20held%20its%20first%20meeting%20at%20the%20Foreign%20Ministry%20Headquarters%20in%20Male'%20on%20Sunday%20morning.%20Indian%20High%20Commissioner%20Munu%20Mahawar%20also%20attended%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENazim%20confirmed%20the%20meeting%20and%20said%20the%20agenda%20for%20the%20meeting%20was%20the%20request%20to%20withdraw%20troops%20by%20March%2015.%20The%20Indian%20government%20did%20not%20immediately%20confirm%20or%20comment%20on%20the%20media%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20Indian%20troops%20from%20Maldives%20was%20a%20key%20election%20promise%20of%20Muizzu.%20It%20recently%20upgraded%20ties%20with%20China%20after%20a%20diplomatic%20row%20between%20India%20and%20Maldives%20erupted%20after%20Maldivian%20ministers%20made%20derogatory%20comments%20against%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20post%20his%20visit%20to%20Lakshadweep%20islands.%20The%20three%20ministers%20were%20sacked%20and%20the%20Maldivian%20Opposition%20criticised%20the%20comments%2C%20but%20the%20President%20said%20%26quot%3Bwe%20may%20be%20small%20but%20no%20one%20has%20the%20license%20to%20bully%20us%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BWorkable%20Solution%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20visited%20the%20Maldives%20in%20November%20and%20met%20the%20current%20President.%20Sources%20in%20the%20Indian%20Government%20told%20NDTV%20earlier%20that%20the%20two%20sides%20agreed%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bworkable%20solution%26quot%3B%20to%20continue%20the%20use%20of%20Indian%20military%20platforms%20by%20the%20island%20nation%20as%20they%20serve%20the%20interests%20of%20its%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20personnel%20operate%20India-sponsored%20radars%20and%20surveillance%20aircraft.%20Indian%20warships%20in%20the%20region%20help%20patrol%20the%20country's%20exclusive%20economic%20zone.%C2%A0Despite%20its%20small%20size%2C%20the%20Maldives%20plays%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20regional%20politics%2C%20particularly%20due%20to%20the%20strategic%20maritime%20passages%20in%20its%20northern%20and%20southern%20parts%2C%20making%20it%20a%20key%20toll%20gate%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Muizzu%20earlier%20acknowledged%20the%20significant%20role%20of%20two%20Indian%20helicopters%2C%20the%20Dhruv%2C%20in%20numerous%20emergency%20medical%20evacuations.%20This%20small%20group%20of%20Indian%20soldiers%20have%20been%20stationed%20in%20the%20Maldives%20for%20several%20years%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20had%20said%20India's%20cooperation%20with%20Maldives%20is%20based%20on%20jointly%20addressing%20shared%20challenges%20and%20priorities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20assistance%20and%20platforms%20have%20contributed%20significantly%20to%20public%20welfare%2C%20humanitarian%20assistance%2C%20disaster%20relief%2C%20and%20in%20combating%20illegal%20maritime%20activities%20in%20the%20island%20nation%2C%20the%20ministry%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20Sudden%20Shift%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20from%20Ibrahim%20Solih's%20(President%20before%20Muizzu)%20%26quot%3BIndia%20First%26quot%3B%20policy%20to%20%26quot%3BIndia%20Out%26quot%3B%20is%20not%20sudden.%20Ibrahim%20Solih's%20predecessor%2C%20Abdullah%20Yameen%2C%20is%20said%20to%20be%20the%20first%20Maldivian%20leader%20who%20started%20the%20campaign%20against%20India%20in%202013%20and%20brought%20the%20island%20nation's%20ties%20closer%20to%20China.%20His%20successor%20Ibrahim%20Solih%20maintained%20friendly%20ties%20with%20India%20during%20his%20tenure%20from%202018%20to%202023.%20The%20role%20of%20social%20media%20and%20Maldives'%20Dhiyares%20News%20is%20considered%20significant%20in%20crafting%20the%20narrative%20against%20India%20during%20Abdullah%20Yameen's%20t