20one%20on%20top%20of%20the%20other%20to%20make%20a%20new%20duplex%20in%20Aurora%2C%20Colorado.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659ffdccdcdb354a9856ac2b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20crane%20taking%20four%2015-foot-wide%20by%2060-foot-long%20modular%20home%20segments%20and%20stacking%20them%20one%20on%20top%20of%20the%20other%20to%20make%20a%20new%20duplex%20in%20Aurora%2C%20Colorado.%3Cp%3EHyoung%20Chang%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EModular%2C%20or%20factory-built%2C%20housing%20could%20help%20boost%20efficiency%20and%20cut%20costs%20in%20the%20homebuilding%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20many%20modular%20construction%20companies%20have%20failed%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20construction%20industry%20expert%20says%20much%20more%20than%20government%20policy%20needs%20to%20change.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFactory-built%20housing%20is%20increasingly%20being%20hailed%20as%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20housing%20shortage%20and%20affordability%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20world%20of%20modular%20housing%2C%20which%20includes%20multi-unit%20apartment%20buildings%20and%20conventional-looking%20houses%2C%20is%20littered%20with%20companies%20that%20have%20gone%20bust.%20One%20of%20these%20was%20Katerra%2C%20a%20SoftBank-backed%20firm%20that%20sought%20to%20be%20a%20one-stop-shop%20for%20factory-made%20buildings.%20After%20investors%20poured%20billions%20of%20dollars%20into%20the%20much-hyped%20company%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fsoftbank-backed-katerra-files-for-chapter-11-11623060434%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiled%20for%20bankruptcy%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMark%20Erlich%2C%20a%20former%20officer%20of%20the%20New%20England%20Regional%20Council%20of%20Carpenters%20and%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.press.uillinois.edu%2Fbooks%2F%3Fid%3Dp087332%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Way%20We%20Build%3A%20Restoring%20Dignity%20to%20Construction%20Work%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20chalks%20many%20of%20the%20failures%20up%20to%20inexperience%20with%20the%20construction%20industry.%20Investors%20from%20outside%20the%20industry%20have%20come%20in%20with%20ambitious%20plans%20to%20disrupt%20it%2C%20but%20little%20of%20the%20expertise%20necessary%20to%20find%20and%20fill%20a%20niche%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKaterra%20was%20started%20by%20guys%20from%20Silicon%20Valley%20who%20were%20going%20to%20show%20the%20stupid%20construction%20industry%20what%20a%20bunch%20of%20dinosaurs%20they%20were%2C%26quot%3B%20Erlich%20said.%20That%20%26quot%3Barrogance%26quot%3B%20built%20the%20foundation%20for%20their%20demise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20slew%20of%20other%20examples%20of%20similar%20failures%20in%20the%20US%20and%20around%20the%20world%2C%20including%20the%20California%20start-up%20Veev%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fproblems-with-prefabricated-homes-why-lennar-bought-veev-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eran%20out%20of%20money%20late%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20UK%20company%20Urban%20Splash's%20modular%20business%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bdonline.co.uk%2Fnews%2Furban-splash-cuts-a-quarter-of-staff-after-modular-collapse%2F5125788.article%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecalled%20House%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20collapsed%20in%202022.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboxabl-tiny-home-casita-production-governance-galiano-paolo-tiramani-spending-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20trendy%20Las%20Vegas%20tiny%20home%20start-up%20Boxabl%20is%20rapidly%20losing%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolicymakers%20and%20housing%20advocates%20are%20looking%20for%20all%20kinds%20of%20potential%20solutions%20to%20the%20housing%20crisis.%20They%20point%20out%20that%20home-building%20productivity%20hasn't%20improved%20much%20in%20decades.%20Constructing%20homes%20in%20factories%20can%20be%20more%20efficient%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jchs.harvard.edu%2Fblog%2Fcomparing-costs-manufactured-and-site-built-housing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eless%20costly%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20than%20traditional%20construction.%20While%20workers%20prepare%20the%20foundation%20on-site%2C%20the%20home%20can%20simultaneously%20be%20constructed%20in%20a%20factory%2C%20without%20weather%20and%20other%20interruptions%20slowing%20down%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFactory%20productivity%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20ways%20that%20we%20build%20cars%2C%20airplanes%2C%20ships%2C%20too%2C%20nowadays%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0has%20increased%20a%20lot%20in%20the%20last%2060%20years%20or%20so.%20And%20so%20being%20able%20to%20unlock%20that%20productivity%20game%20in%20the%20residential%20space%20can%20and%20should%20bring%20costs%20back%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Andrew%20Justus%2C%20a%20housing%20policy%20analyst%20at%20the%20Niskanen%20Center%2C%20a%20nonpartisan%20think%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20layers%20of%20restrictive%20government%20regulations%2C%20including%20zoning%20laws%20and%20building%20codes%2C%20often%20stand%20in%20the%20way%20of%20more%20factory-made%20homes.%20The%20complex%20web%20of%20local%20and%20state%20regulations%20can%20make%20it%20impossible%20for%20modular%20home%20companies%20to%20build%20the%20economies%20of%20scale%20they%20need%20to%20bring%20down%20costs%20and%20turn%20a%20profit%2C%20Justus%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20restrictive%20policies%20often%20reflect%20the%20lingering%20perception%20that%20factory-built%20homes%20are%20inferior%20to%20traditional%20housing%2C%20Erlich%20said.%20There's%20a%20stigma%20around%20trailers%20or%20mobile%20homes%2C%20which%20the%20federal%20government%20defines%20as%20manufactured%20housing%20built%20before%201976.%20The%20modern%20versions%20of%20this%20housing%20are%20still%20widely%20considered%20unappealing%2C%20he%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20government%20has%20made%20some%20efforts%20to%20cut%20red%20tape%20for%20factory-built%20housing.%20The%20Biden%20administration%20proposed%20loosening%20the%20Department%20of%20Housing%20and%20Urban%20Development%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hud.gov%2Fpress%2Fpress_releases_media_advisories%2Fhud_no_22_133%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eregulations%20on%20manufactured%20housing%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20increase%20the%20supply%2C%20including%20by%20legalizing%20up%20to%20three%20units%20per%20factory-built%20structure.%20But%20cities%20and%20states%20would%20need%20to%20liberalize%20their%20own%20regulations%20to%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20more%20of%20these%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EObstacles%20for%20the%20modular%20housing%20industry%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EErlich%20said%20the%20policy%20landscape%20isn't%20the%20most%20significant%20obstacle%20for%20the%20industry.%20More%20important%2C%20he%20argues%2C%20is%20the%20lack%20of%20consistent%20demand%20for%20modular%20buildings%2C%20the%20high%20costs%20of%20transporting%20a%20finished%20product%20to%20the%20building%20site%2C%20and%20the%20decentralized%20nature%20of%20construction.%20While%20the%20timeline%20for%20modular%20construction%20is%20consistently%20compressed%2C%20transportation%20and%20other%20costs%20can%20mean%20it%20isn't%20cheaper%20than%20building%20on-site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20aren't%20convinced%20there's%20sufficient%20and%20consistent%20demand%20for%20modular%20housing%20in%20most%20markets.%20Modular%20construction%20is%20best%20for%20buildings%20that%20have%20repeated%20components%2C%20like%20a%20hotel%20with%20hundreds%20of%20identical%20rooms%2C%20a%20dorm%20building%2C%20or%20a%20multi-family%20apartment%20building%20with%20identical%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20to%20adjust%20for%20design%20details%2C%20at%20that%20point%20it%20just%20becomes%20prohibitively%20expensive%2C%20and%20you're%20much%20better%20off%20to%20build%20it%20on-site%2C%26quot%3B%20Erlich%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20the%20right%20market%2C%20there%20aren't%20many%20willing%20investors%20within%20the%20construction%20industry.%20This%20is%20partly%20because%20the%20sector%20is%20so%20decentralized%3A%20construction%20managers%20outsource%20much%20of%20the%20work%2C%20and%20subcontractors%20generally%20don't%20have%20the%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20have%20a%20General%20Motors%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20Tesla%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20somebody%20who's%20willing%20to%20spend%20ten%20years%20before%20they%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Erlich%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFailures%20and%20successes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20failed%20companies%2C%20some%20messy%20major%20modular%20projects%20have%20also%20drawn%20attention%20to%20the%20industry's%20problems.%20A%2032-story%20modular%20apartment%20building%20in%20Brooklyn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fmodular-building-believed-to-be-worlds-tallest-makes-debut-in-brooklyn-1479261926%3Fmod%3Darticle_inline%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etook%20four%20years%20to%20construct%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20legal%20disputes%20and%20other%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Manhattan%2C%20a%20project%20that%20was%20supposed%20to%20become%20the%20tallest%20modular%20hotel%20in%20the%20world%20was%20scheduled%20to%20be%20finished%20in%20late%202020.%20But%20the%20pandemic%20and%20a%20shortage%20of%20funding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fa-supertall-modular-hotel-is-going-up-in-manhattan-if-the-rooms-ever-leave-brooklyn-11623153600%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparalyzed%20construction%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20all%20168%20fully%20pre-fabricated%20and%20furnished%20hotel%20rooms%20sit%20on%20a%20dock%20in%20Brooklyn.%20In%20late%20December%202023%2C%20the%20hotel's%20lender%2C%20Avana%20Capital%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pincusco.com%2F33m-pre-foreclosure-at-worlds-tallest-modular-hotel-dev-site-in-nomad%2F%3Flp_txn_id%3D305276%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiled%20a%20%2433%20million%20pre-foreclosure%20action%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Manhattan%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20have%20found%20a%20way%20to%20succeed%20in%20the%20space.%20They%20tend%20to%20be%20run%20by%20people%20with%20deep%20experience%20in%20the%20construction%20industry%2C%20Erlich%20said.%20A%20newer%20example%20is%20Factory%20OS%2C%20a%20firm%20in%20the%20San%20Francisco%20Bay%20Area%20created%20by%20established%20developers%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20region's%20carpenters%20union%20that's%20delivering%20on%20the%20area's%20demand%20for%20factory-built%20affordable%20housing%2C%20while%20also%20doing%20some%20on-site%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20started%20with%20a%20higher%20degree%20of%20expertise%20and%20experience%20in%20the%20housing%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Erlich%20said%20of%20Factory%20OS.%20%26quot%3BThey%20knew%20where%20the%20demand%20was%20and%20how%20they%20could%20satisfy%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFactory%20OS%20has%20plans%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2021%2F09%2F10%2Frealestate%2Fprefabricated-modular-apartments.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpand%20its%20reach%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20California%2C%20but%20appreciates%20the%20localized%20nature%20of%20the%20construction%20industry%20and%20isn't%20looking%20to%20open%20factories%20across%20the%20country%2C%20its%20co-founder%20told%20The%20New%20York%20Times.%20And%20that%20approach%20could%20be%20the%20key%20to%20its%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20in%20the%20modular%20housing%20industry%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aerelman%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eerelman%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcheap-starter-homes-manufactured-modular-housing-failing-real-estate-construction-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705232581000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659ffea0dcdb354a9856acf4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcheap-starter-homes-manufactured-modular-housing-failing-real-estate-construction-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Factory-built%20homes%20could%20help%20solve%20the%20housing%20affordability%20crisis%2C%20but%20the%20companies%20attempting%20to%20disrupt%20the%20construction%20industry%20are%20failing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Eliza%20Relman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcheap-starter-homes-manufactured-modular-housing-failing-real-estate-construction-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Asked%20Nehra%20For%20A%20Job%20At%20Gujarat%20Titans%20But%20He%20Declined%2C'%20Claims%20Yuvraj%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20all-rounder%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yuvraj%20Singh%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F456-yuvraj-singh-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYuvraj%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20denied%20a%20role%20in%20the%20Gujarat%20Titans%20team.%20While%20indicating%20he%20would%20like%20to%20be%20a%20mentor%20of%20an%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20side%2C%20Yuvraj%20revealed%20that%20he%20tried%20to%20ask%20Gujarat%20Titans%20head%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ashish%20Nehra%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F324-ashish-nehra-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAshish%20Nehra%3C