%20notches%20below%20the%20season's%20average.%20The%20weather%20department%20has%20predicted%20very%20dense%20fog%20and%20cold%20wave%20conditions%20for%20more%20two%20days%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20fog%2C%20the%20air%20quality%20has%20also%20dipped%20in%20Delhi%20and%20surrounding%20areas.%20To%20combat%20that%2C%20the%20Centre%20today%20mandated%20the%20enforcement%20of%20anti-pollution%20measures%20classified%20under%20Stage-III%20of%20the%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20(GRAP)%20across%20Delhi-NCR%20with%20immediate%20effect%20with%20immediate%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20restrictions%20imposed%20under%20GRAP%20Stage-III%20puts%20a%20stop%20to%20operations%20in%20stone%20crushers%20and%20all%20mining%20and%20related%20activities%20in%20the%20NCR.%20Additionally%2C%20a%20strict%20ban%20on%20construction%20and%20demolition%20activities%20has%20been%20implemented%20throughout%20the%20region%2C%20albeit%20with%20certain%20exemptions%20for%20specific%20project%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705222440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fik4lgjeg_school-cold-winters-pti_625x300_28_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-schools-to-reopen-tomorrow-after-winter-break-4860620%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Schools%20in%20Delhi%20are%20set%20to%20reopen%20tomorrow%2C%20resuming%20classes%20in%20physical%20mode.%20However%2C%20acknowledging%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20cold%20weather%2C%20the%20government%20has%20implemented%20adjustments%20to%20school%20timings%20to%20mitigate%20the%20impact%20on%20students.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-schools-to-reopen-tomorrow-after-winter-break-4860620%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-schools-to-reopen-tomorrow-after-