%20a%20journey%20that%20would%20see%20him%20serve%20as%20Mumbai's%20mayor%20and%20eventually%20shape%20the%20political%20landscape%20of%20South%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201970s%2C%20when%20Congress%20faced%20setbacks%20both%20at%20the%20national%20and%20state%20levels%2C%20Mr%20Deora%20emerged%20as%20a%20key%20figure.%20A%20split%20engineered%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20Progressive%20Democratic%20Front%20with%20the%20Janata%20Party%2C%20marked%20a%20challenging%20period%20for%20Congress.%20Despite%20having%20no%20aspirations%20for%20ministerial%20roles%2C%20Murli%20Deora%20assumed%20the%20role%20of%20president%20of%20the%20Bombay%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee%2C%20a%20position%20he%20held%20for%20over%20two%20decades.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20veteran%20was%20also%20a%20close%20confidant%20of%20prime%20minister%20Rajiv%20Gandhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fmvtseahg_murli-deora-rajiv-gandhi_625x300_14_January_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETasked%20with%20the%20role%20of%20a%20bridge%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20city's%20corporate%20elite%2C%20he%20facilitated%20the%20smooth%20flow%20of%20funds%20to%20the%20party.%20His%20relationships%20with%20industrial%20magnates%20like%20the%20Birlas%20and%20Dhirubhai%20Ambani%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20sustaining%20the%20party's%20financial%20machinery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhenever%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20visited%20Mumbai%2C%20Murli%20Deora%20organised%20lunches%20at%20the%20Cricket%20Club%20of%20India%2C%20an%20event%20that%20drew%20journalists%20and%20prominent%20personalities%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20the%20baton%20of%20South%20Mumbai's%20representation%20was%20passed%20on%20to%20his%20son%2C%20Milind%2C%20as%20the%20senior%20Deora%20continued%20to%20exert%20influence%20behind%20the%20scenes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh's%20today%20described%20Murli%20Deora%20as%20a%20stalwart%20Congressman%20who%20stood%20by%20the%20party%20through%20thick%20and%20thin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMilind%20Deora's%20Exit%2C%20And%20Its%20Impact%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20tributes%20flowed%2C%20the%20departure%20of%20Milind%20Deora%20from%20the%20Congress%20has%20raised%20questions%20on%20how%20the%20move%20could%20affect%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20is%20already%20in%20a%20tight%20position%2C%20discussing%20seat-sharing%20plans%20with%20multiple%20parties%20across%20states%2C%20be%20it%20with%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee-led%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20government%20in%20West%20Bengal%20or%20the%20Bhagwant%20Mann-led%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20government%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F11-big-exits-from-congress-as-party-plans-big-for-2024-polls-4860027%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi's%20Vanishing%20Team%3A%2011%20Leaders%20Who%20Quit%20Congress%20Since%202019%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20general%20elections%20scheduled%20this%20year%2C%20the%20party%20walks%20on%20a%20tightrope%2C%20trying%20to%20avoid%20embarrassing%20situations%20like%20Sachin%20Pilot's%20rebellion%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20a%20state%20which%20they%20lost%20in%20the%20recently%20held%20assembly%20elections.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20news%20of%20Milind%20Deora's%20exit%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20announcement%20of%20his%20resignation%2C%20just%20before%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20-%20a%20mega%20Congress%20outreach%20rally%20-%20was%20determined%20by%20Prime%20Minister