the-gandhi-deora-ties-and-how-milind-deoras-exit-impacts-congress-4860362%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-gandhi-deora-ties-and-how-milind-deoras-exit-impacts-congress-4860362%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-gandhi-deora-ties-and-how-milind-deoras-exit-impacts-congress-4860362%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pollution%20Curbs%20Back%20In%20Delhi%20As%20Air%20Quality%20Dips%20To%20'Severe'%20Category%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20today%20mandated%20the%20enforcement%20of%20anti-pollution%20measures%20classified%20under%20Stage-III%20of%20the%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20(GRAP)%20across%20Delhi-NCR%20with%20immediate%20effect%20with%20immediate%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board's%20(CPCB)%20Sub-Committee%20on%20Clean%20Air%20and%20Sustainable%20Mobility%20has%20determined%20the%20necessity%20of%20invoking%20an%208-point%20action%20plan%20in%20alignment%20with%20Stage-III%20of%20GRAP%20across%20the%20entire%20National%20Capital%20Region%20to%20curb%20the%20further%20deterioration%20of%20air%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20restrictions%20imposed%20under%20GRAP%20Stage-III%20puts%20a%20stop%20to%20operations%20in%20stone%20crushers%20and%20all%20mining%20and%20related%20activities%20in%20the%20NCR.%20Additionally%2C%20a%20strict%20ban%20on%20construction%20and%20demolition%20activities%20has%20been%20implemented%20throughout%20the%20region%2C%20albeit%20with%20certain%20exemptions%20for%20specific%20project%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ECAQM%20Sub-Committee%20for%20operationalization%20of%20GRAP%20called%20on%20an%20emergency%20meeting%20today%20morning%20in%20view%20of%20sudden%20deterioration%20of%20air%20quality%20of%20Delhi-NCR%20from%20la