%20I%20can%20maybe%20teach%20him%20is%20how%20to%20hold%20a%20bat%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Virat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20Virat%20wished%20Djokovic%20the%20very%20best%20for%20the%20Australian%20Open%2C%20where%20Djokovic%20is%20defending%20his%20men's%20singles%20title.%20He%20also%20told%20Djokovic%20that%20Australia%20is%20personally%20his%20favourite%20place%20to%20play%20cricket%20and%20the%20tennis%20star%20will%20enjoy%20the%20support%20from%20the%20Aussie%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNovak%20I%20would%20like%20to%20wish%20you%20the%20very%20best%20for%20the%20Australian%20Open.%20I%20know%20how%20excited%20and%20prepared%20you%20are%20for%20these%20big%20events%2C%20these%20grand%20slams.%20I%20have%20no%20doubt%20that%20we%20will%20see%20Djokovic%20we%20have%20seen%20over%20the%20years.%20I%20hope%20you%20have%20a%20great%20tournament.%20Australia%20is%20a%20lovely%20place%20to%20visit%20and%20play%20a%20tournament.%20It%20is%20my%20favourite%20place%20to%20play%20cricket.%20The%20love%20and%20support%20from%20Australians%20is%20something%20great%2C%20as%20they%20appreciate%20true%20sportsmanship%20and%20fierce%20competition%2C%20which%20you%20have%20in%20abundance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%20starting%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Djokovic%20had%20also%20talked%20about%20his%20bond%20with%20Virat%20and%20described%20a%20trip%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20Sony%20Sports%20Network%2C%20Djokovic%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BVirat%20Kohli%20and%20I%20have%20been%20texting%20a%20little%20bit%20for%20a%20few%20years%20and%20we%20never%20got%20the%20chance%20to%20meet%20in%20person.%20But%20it%20was%20really%20a%20privilege%20and%20honour%20to%20listen%20to%20him%20speak%20nicely%20about%20me%20and%20I%20obviously%20admire%20his%20career%2C%20and%20achievement%20and%20everything%20he%20has%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20to%20India%20only%20once%20so%20far%20in%20my%20life.%20It%20was%2C%20I%20think%2C%2010%20or%2011%20years%20ago.%20I%20came%20to%20play%20an%20exhibition%20event%20in%20New%20Delhi%20for%20two%20days.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20short%20stay.%20So%2C%20I%20really%20hope%20that%20I%20will%20be%20able%20to%20come%20back%20in%20the%20near%20future%2C%20too%2C%20because%20I%20have%20a%20great%20desire%20and%20a%20great%20wish%20to%20explore%20your%20beautiful%20country%2C%20which%20has%20so%20much%20history%2C%20so%20much%20culture%20to%20offer%20the%20world%20and%20so%20much%20spirituality%20as%20well.%20It%20is%20amazing%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2036-year-old%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Djokovic%20and%20Virat%20are%20the%20legends%20of%20their%20sports.%20Djokovic%20is%20a%2024-time%20Grand%20Slam%20champion%2C%20the%20most%20by%20a%20male%20tennis%20star.%20If%20he%20wins%20his%20record-extending%2011th%20Australian%20Open%20title%2C%20this%20will%20be%20his%2025th%20Grand%20Slam%20title%2C%20which%20will%20break%20the%20record%20of%20Australia's%20Margaret%20Court%2C%20who%20also%20has%2024%20major%20titles.%3Cbr%3E%5CnVirat%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20won%20the%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202011%20and%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20with%20India.%20He%20is%20the%20only%20player%20to%20have%20smashed%2050%20ODI%20centuries.%20He%20has%20also%20won%20'Player%20of%20the%20Tournament'%20in%20the%20ICC%20T20%20World%20Cup%202014%20and%202016%20and%20the%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20in%20India%20for%20his%20remarkable%20batting%20performances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20crowned%20the%20'ICC%20Cricketer%20of%20the%20Decade'%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20520%20matches%2C%20he%20has%20scored%2026%2C704%20runs%20(8%2C848%20in%20Tests%2C%2013%2C848%20in%20ODIs%20and%204%2C008%20in%20T20Is)%20at%20an%20average%20of%2054.27%20across%20all%20formats%2C%20with%2080%20centuries%20and%20139%20fifties.%20His%20best%20score%20is%20254*.%20He%20is%20the%20fourth-hig