d%20by%20the%20US%20government%E2%80%99s%20argument%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fus-court-denies-guptas-plea-for-defence-material-580836%5C%22%3EGupta%20did%20not%20yet%20have%20the%20right%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20provided%20with%20the%20case%20materials%20and%20evidence%20he%20sought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20earlier%20report%20by%20the%20news%20agency%2C%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20attorney%20argued%20that%20his%20lawyers%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20%E2%80%93%20where%20he%20has%20been%20jailed%20since%20June%20%E2%80%93%20were%20unable%20to%20secure%20his%20rights%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20information%20on%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20defence%20counsel%20present%20in%20Prague%20has%20no%20evidence%20or%20other%20case%20materials%20other%20than%20the%20bare%20indictment%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20counsel%20in%20the%20US%20Jeff%20Chabrowe%20told%20the%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fnews%2Fworld%2F2024%2F01%2F11%2Fpannun-case-us-objects-to-providing-defence-material-to-nikhil-gupta-till-his-appearance-in-ny-court.html%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20PTI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChabrowe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CMost%20critically%2C%20the%20defendant%20continues%20(to%20be)%20interrogated%20by%20US%20officials%2C%20after%20the%20indictment%2C%20where%20his%20uninformed%20counsel%20has%20no%20ability%20to%20secure%20his%20rights.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAccordingly%2C%20this%20court%20should%20order%20the%20government%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20defence%20discovery%20request%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20request%20for%20%E2%80%98discovery%E2%80%99%20refers%20to%20a%20request%20to%20the%20prosecution%20to%20share%20certain%20case%20materials%20and%20evidence%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao%2Fjustice-101%2Fdiscovery%5C%22%3Eahead%20of%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistrict%20Judge%20Marrero