523%2Fknya-med-couple-makes-eco-friendly-recycled-polyester-scrubs-for-doctors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emedical%20equipment%20%3C%2Fa%3Elike%20wheelchairs%2C%20walking%20sticks%2C%20and%20medical%20beds%20lying%20unused%20in%20our%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognising%20that%20such%20items%20could%20be%20valuable%20to%20those%20who%20cannot%20afford%20new%20equipment%2C%20Ajayan%20Namminipurthu%2C%20based%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20initiated%20a%20non-profit%20organisation%20called%20Sanathya%20Foundation%2C%20which%20collects%20gently%20used%20items%20from%20donors%20and%20provides%20them%20for%20free%20to%20individuals%20in%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20demand%20for%20such%20equipment%20is%20not%20limited%20to%20the%20elderly%3B%20anyone%20might%20require%20them.%20My%20foundation%20aims%20to%20assist%20individuals%20who%20cannot%20afford%20these%20items%20such%20as%20nebulisers%2C%20walkers%2C%20beds%2C%20and%20I%20ship%20the%20equipment%20to%20them%20without%20any%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20adding%20that%20his%20foundation%20has%20helped%20over%2085%20people%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWill%20to%20do%20something%20for%20the%20society%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Ajayan%20relocated%20to%20Bengaluru%20in%201999%20in%20pursuit%20of%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20came%20to%20the%20city%20for%20a%20job%20and%20instantly%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20it.%20The%20climate%20and%20the%20rich%20culture%20motivated%20me%20to%20establish%20a%20life%20here.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20working%20in%20the%20corporate%20sector%20ever%20since%2C%20building%20a%20home%20and%20a%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20building%20his%20life%20in%20the%20city%2C%20there%20came%20a%20point%20when%20Ajayan%20desired%20to%20contribute%20to%20society%20by%20going%20beyond%20the%20routine.%20%E2%80%9CSooner%20or%20later%2C%20everyone%20experiences%20the%20urge%20to%20do%20something%20more%20meaningful.%20After%20working%20for%20numerous%20years%2C%20I%20felt%20the%20need%20to%20make%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F229014%2Findia-farmer-agriculture-reforms-central-government-nirmala-sitharaman-essential-commodities-act-contract-farming-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20positive%20impact%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20society.%20This%20idea%2C%20once%20planted%2C%20lingered%20with%20me%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20make%20a%20New%20Year%20resolution%20to%20serve%20society.%20%E2%80%9CI%20happened%20to%20visit%20an%20orphanage%20located%20on%20Mysore%20Road.%20Despite%20being%20well-run%2C%20it%20lacked%20several%20amenities%2C%20and%20there%20were%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20children.%20When%20I%20visited%20in%20January%2C%20considering%20the%20climate%20in%20Bangalore%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20area%2C%20I%20noticed%20the%20children%20were%20sleeping%20on%20the%20floor.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-2-1704891555.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sanathya%20Foundation%20provides%20free%20medical%20equipment%20to%20people%20in%20need%20for%20free.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-2-1704891555.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-2-1704891555-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-2-1704891555-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-2-1704891555-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-2-1704891555-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-337929%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESanathya%20Foundation%20provides%20free%20medical%20equipment%20to%20people%20in%20need%20for%20free.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Ajayan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20witnessing%20the%20children%20sleeping%20on%20the%20floor%20touched%20his%20heart%2C%20prompting%20him%20to%20take%20action%20and%20organise%20beds%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20that%20providing%20the%20beds%20would%20be%20a%20significant%20investment%20for%20me%20alone.%20This%20led%20me%20to%20turn%20to%20Facebook%20in%20search%20of%20more%20people%20willing%20to%20participate.%20I%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20to%20find%20that%20many%20individuals%20were%20eager%20to%20contribute%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20experience%20served%20as%20inspiration%20for%20him%20to%20do%20more%20in%20the%20future.%20%E2%80%9CI%20yearned%20to%20engage%20in%20more%20activities%20like%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20turning%20point%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ajayan%20kept%20an%20eye%20on%20such%20opportunities%2C%20it%20was%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20illness%20that%20made%20him%20think%20of%20establishing%20the%20Sanathya%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202015%2C%20my%20father%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333669%2Fbasic-health-tests-we-should-do-regularly-heart-lungs-kidneys-cancer-detection-inspiring-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehad%20a%20stroke%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Kerala%2C%20so%20I%20brought%20him%20here.%20During%20his%20recovery%2C%20he%20experienced%20another%20fall%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20broken%20thigh.%20This%20incident%20required%20us%20to%20admit%20him%20to%20the%20hospital%20once%20again%2C%20where%20he%20underwent%20surgery.%20Following%20the%20surgical%20procedure%2C%20we%20had%20to%20purchase%20a%20medical%20bed%20as%20he%20was%20on%20complete%20bed%20rest%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjayan%E2%80%99s%20father%20remained%20bedridden%20for%20several%20weeks%2C%20undergoing%20physiotherapy%20and%20various%20treatments.%20%E2%80%9CGradually%2C%20his%20condition%20improved%2C%20allowing%20him%20to%20transition%20to%20a%20wheelchair.%20After%20about%20a%20month%2C%20he%20progressed%20to%20using%20a%20walker%20and%20eventually%20a%20walking%20stick%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20he%20used%20the%20walking%20stick%20until%20the%20end%2C%20the%20other%20equipment%20became%20redundant.%20It%E2%80%99s%20impractical%20to%20keep%20a%20large%20bed%20at%20home%20when%20it%E2%80%99s%20no%20longer%20needed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjayan%20also%20realised%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20these%20items%20was%20quite%20expensive%20and%20might%20be%20unaffordable%20to%20many.%20%E2%80%9CI%20approached%20the%20sellers%20of%20these%20types%20of%20equipment%20and%20inquired%20whether%20they%20would%20take%20them%20back%20or%20if%20there%20was%20someone%20else%20in%20need.%20Surprisingly%2C%20they%20declined%2C%20suggesting%20I%20either%20give%20them%20to%20a%20scrap%20collector%20or%20to%20my%20local%20newspaper%20vendor%2C%20who%20could%20sell%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjayan%20did%20not%20want%20to%20sell%20the%20items%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310812%2Fmukul-chhabra-scrapuncle-delhi-startup-collects-recycles-scrap-wins-lakhs-shark-tank%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escrap%20collector%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20decided%20to%20think%2