0%E2%80%9CThe%20bus%20first%20touched%20me%20and%20I%20fell%20down%2C%20after%20which%20a%20tyre%20rode%20over%20my%20right%20leg.%20Luckily%2C%20I%20was%20wearing%20heels%20that%20day%2C%20due%20to%20which%2C%20some%20of%20the%20pressure%20was%20absorbed%20by%20it.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20remember%20what%20happened%20after%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20Veena%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20right%20leg%20was%20so%20badly%20affected%20that%20she%20had%20to%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20in%20the%20hospital.%20Doctors%20tried%20different%20ways%20to%20help%20salvage%20her%20foot%2C%20but%20three%20surgeries%20failed%2C%20and%20finally%2C%20a%20skin%20graft%20was%20performed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20I%20was%20a%20growing%20child%2C%20attempts%20by%20doctors%20to%20use%20flesh%20from%20my%20left%20thigh%20to%20rebuild%20my%20foot%20failed.%20They%20tried%20unsuccessfully%20three%20times%20and%20found%20that%20nothing%20worked.%20They%20finally%20grafted%20some%20skin%20and%20told%20me%20that%20I%20had%20to%20live%20with%20it.%20It%E2%80%99s%20still%20very%20delicate%20and%20I%20have%20to%20bandage%20it%20daily%20before%20stepping%20out.%20I%20was%20bedridden%20for%20six%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fveena-1704806494.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Veena%20runs%20Kari%20dosa%20food%20cart%20in%20Bengaluru%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fveena-1704806494.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fveena-1704806494-240x300.jpeg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fveena-1704806494-500x625.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media